<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> dilīpayyaṁ Īṟi
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vanoḻaṁba rājyaṁgeyyuttire
<lb n="3"/>keṁgūra mahājana mūnūrbbaru
<lb n="4"/>pasuṇḍibōvara duggaseṭṭige tuṁ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>bbiḍisuvandu koṭṭa stiti Āvude
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ndaḍe keṟeya keḻage talerā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>siyali bittalaṭṭeyuṁ kha
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṇḍuga gaḻdeyuṁ keṟe
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ge salgu
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="10"/>keṟeya keḻagaṇa bitta
<lb n="11" break="no"/>laṭṭeyuva khaṇḍuga gaḻde
<lb n="12" break="no"/>yuva keṟege naḍeyisuvo
<lb n="13"/>naḍayisadaḍe keṟeyuṁ dēgu
<lb n="14" break="no"/>lavuṁ pasuvuṁ pārvaruṁ
<lb n="15"/>kavileyuṁ bāṇarāsi
<lb n="16" break="no"/>yuvanaḻida pāpaṁ sārggu
<lb n="17"/>Ikkuvara bārisada
<lb n="18" break="no"/>rgge pāpavakke bittala
<lb n="19" break="no"/>ṭṭeya bhattava keṟegikku
<lb n="20" break="no"/>vannegaṁ Okkala kayya
<lb n="21" break="no"/>lippuvu <g type="ddanda">.</g>
</p>

